annotations: Amaryllis is a genus of lily native to South Africa and associated in Victorian floriography with “pride, determination, and radiant beauty”. Qualities which Shelly surely has.
Probably a nod to Nicki Minaj’s 2010 track “Your Love” whose chorus starts with the line “Shorty, I'ma only tell you this once, you the illest”

She looks like Shelly in the diner
 She’s got the red lip liner
 She leans her weight against the counter
A reference to the Twin Peaks character Shelly Johnson, played by Mädchen Amick. Shelly works at the Double R Diner and usually wears read lipstick.
